{"id":717596399,"lang":"javascript","lang_name":"JavaScript","time":"1Â year","timestamp":1654720583,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"107 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/717596399/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Reverse Vowels of a String","memory":"49.8 MB","code":"/**\n * @param {string} s\n * @return {string}\n */\nvar reverseVowels = function(s) {\n    let vowels = new Set(['a','e','i','o','u'])\n    const arr = s.split('')\n    \n    let left = 0, right = s.length-1\n    \n    while(left < right){\n      const lc = arr[left].toLowerCase()     \n      const rc = arr[right].toLowerCase()\n      \n      if(vowels.has(lc) && vowels.has(rc)){\n          \n        [arr[left], arr[right]] = [arr[right], arr[left]];\n        left++;\n        right--;        \n      }\n        \n      if(!vowels.has(lc)){\n        left++\n      }else if(!vowels.has(rc)){\n        right--\n      }\n    }\n    \n    return arr.join('')\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"reverse-vowels-of-a-string","has_notes":false}
